snippet.title: First Victory Royale - Twitch Plays Conway's Game of Life - Battle Royale Edition
snippet.description:
Play Conway's Game of Life by typing commands in the Twitch chat: https://www.twitch.tv/bzh314
The first Victory Royale in Twitch Plays Conway's Game of Life was won by @qwertyasdfuiopghjkl (https://www.twitch.tv/qwertyasdfuiopghjkl). A victory so sweeping the storm didn't even have time to form yet! Mainly because @Skystrike55 (https://www.twitch.tv/skystrike55) didn't stick the landing, but don't tell anyone.

More:
* VOD with chat commands: https://www.twitch.tv/videos/356111749
* Homepage of Twitch Plays Conway's Game of Life: https://bzh314.com/twitch_plays_conway_game_of_life/
* TPCGOL is built with the Unity3d Entity Component System (ECS), Burst Compiler and C# Job System
* Play Now on #Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/bzh314

#Twitch #Unity3D #Fortnite #IndieGame #GameDev
